#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:2
msgid "CLI Reference"
msgstr "CLI 命令参考"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:4
msgid "The short command is ``anna``. The longer alias ``anna-agent`` is also available."
msgstr "短命令是 ``anna``，兼容别名是 ``anna-agent``。"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:7
msgid "Global Commands"
msgstr "全局命令"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:18
msgid "``doctor`` checks the local AnnaAgent installation, workspace settings, and common runtime requirements. Run it before expensive experiments."
msgstr "``doctor`` 会检查安装、workspace 配置和常见运行条件。正式实验前建议先运行。"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:22
msgid "Assets"
msgstr "资产"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:31
msgid "Always pass ``--workspace`` or ``--manifest`` so downloads go to the intended workspace. If you omit both, the current directory becomes the workspace."
msgstr "下载资产时始终传 ``--workspace`` 或 ``--manifest``，避免下载到错误目录。"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:35
msgid "Models"
msgstr "模型"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:47
msgid "Use ``models deploy`` for local vLLM services. See :doc:`deployment`."
msgstr "本地 vLLM 部署见 :doc:`deployment`。"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:50
msgid "Data"
msgstr "数据"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:60
msgid "Memory"
msgstr "记忆"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:71
msgid "Initialization"
msgstr "初始化"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:87
msgid "``prompt-only`` is fast and uses a single frozen prompt. ``full`` runs the full AnnaAgent initialization pipeline and may call multiple model services."
msgstr "``prompt-only`` 快，适合冻结单个 prompt。``full`` 会运行完整初始化流水线，可能调用多个模型服务。"

#: ../../en/cli-reference.rst:91
msgid "Runs and Logs"
msgstr "运行与日志"
